OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy showers, possibly
OL,6,Fthundery, to the north will move off
OL,7,Fthrough the morning, along with any
OL,8,Fhigh cloud. Another hot, dry and sunny
OL,9,Fday for many with some lower cloud
OL,10,Falong northern coasts later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome patchy low cloud will
OL,13,Fcover many of the hills to the north.
OL,14,FLight rain here in the early morning.
OL,15,FA cooler night for some but staying
OL,16,Fquite muggy.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSaturday:FA cloudy start for many but
OL,19,Fwill lift and break through the day.
OL,20,FStaying hot and dry but temperatures
OL,21,Fslightly down on recent days.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
